 “声音”歌手瑞安·怀特·马洛尼（Ryan Whyte Maloney）去世，享年44岁https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-voice-singer-ryan-whyte-whyte-dies-age--44-3832773?utm_source=rsss＆utm_medium = rsss＆utm_medium = rsm_campaign年龄44岁Tom SkinnerWed, 29 Jan 2025 09:53:57 +0000 Music NewsNewsTV News..Let’s Talk – mental healthPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3832773 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/RyanWhyteMaloney-The-Voice.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="瑞安·怀特·马洛尼（Ryan Whyte Maloney）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/RyanWhyteMaloney-The-Voice.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/RyanWhyteMaloney-The-Voice-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/RyanWhyteMaloney-The-Voice-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/RyanWhyteMaloney-The-Voice-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/RyanWhyteMaloney-The-Voice-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/RyanWhyteMaloney-The-Voice-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>他在美国版的演出中由布莱克·谢尔顿（Blake Shelton）执教</p><p>帖子<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-voice-singer-ryan-whyte-dies-aged-44-3832773">“ The Voice”歌手Ryan Whyte Maloney去世，现年44岁，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/RyanWhyteMaloney-The-Voice.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="瑞安·怀特·马洛尼（Ryan Whyte Maloney）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/RyanWhyteMaloney-The-Voice.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/RyanWhyteMaloney-The-Voice-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/RyanWhyteMaloney-The-Voice-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/RyanWhyteMaloney-The-Voice-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/RyanWhyteMaloney-The-Voice-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/RyanWhyteMaloney-The-Voice-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>出现在<em>我们声音</em>上的瑞安·怀特·马洛尼（Ryan Whyte Maloney）享年44岁。</p><p>根据拉斯维加斯的克拉克县验尸官的说法，这位歌手和音乐家自杀死亡（通过<a href="https://people.com/voice-alum-ryan-whyte-maloney-dead-age-44-suicide-8781777" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>人民</em></a>）。死因裁判官将死亡原因列为头部的枪伤。</p><p>怀特·马洛尼（Whyte Maloney）是2014年美国版《现实人才》（The Reality Walth）演出《 <em>The Voice》</em> （The Voice the Voice）的参赛者。他由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blake-shelton">布雷克·谢尔顿（Blake Shelton）</a>执教，并成为乡村歌手兼词曲作者的前五名入围者之一。</p><p>在他的盲目试镜中，已故的歌手从谢尔顿（Shelton），亚当·莱文（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/adam-levine">Adam Levine），乌斯（Adam Levine）</a> ，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/usher">乌瑟（</a> Adam Levine）和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shakira">沙基拉（Shakira）</a>赢得了四主椅子，以<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/journey">撰写</a>“灯光”的封面。</p><p> Whyte Maloney在季后赛回合中被NBC唱歌大赛淘汰，在Shineown表演了“第二次机会”之后。后来他在那年的第六季大结局中回到了<em>声音</em>。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="瑞安·怀特·马洛尼（Ryan Whyte Maloney）“灯光”第6季的声音" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/qoOwpCB-VE0?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>他与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/morgan-wallen">摩根·沃伦（Morgan Wallen）</a>在同一赛季参加了该计划。</p><p>这位歌手于1981年出生于密歇根州特拉弗斯市，长大后弹吉他，鼓，大提琴和小提琴。他出现在prog-Rock乐队的主持人中。 2015年，他在10年后离开了该小组，从事个人职业。</p><p>后来他发行了首张个人专辑《我去过的地方》。怀特·马洛尼（Whyte Maloney）还分享了曲目“ Hillbilly”，“ Michigan Moonlight”和“无方向生活”，这些曲目是在美国乡村广播电台播出的。</p><p>本月初，怀特·马洛尼（Whyte Maloney）通过分享了他在Instagram上的<em>声音</em>中分享一篇文章，标记了他的生日。他<a style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;" href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DE4xgxgRGtQ/?hl=en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">写道</a>：“当有机会展示我在<em>声音</em>上的才华时，我在拍摄过程中处于可怕的状态。”</p><p> “在经济上挣扎，诉诸于缩小的废料，从酒店垃圾和走廊上寄养，而周围的人像度假一样狂热地与家人狂欢，我站在那儿，恐惧，只是生存。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DE7WVfZpgFQ/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 52