LadyGagabiggestrisk-music-story-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/LadyGagabiggestrisk-music-story-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/LadyGagabiggestrisk-music-story-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lady-gaga">Lady Gaga</a>透露了她认为是她在音乐生涯中承担的“最大风险”。</p><p>在对<a href="https://www.elle.com/uk/life-and-culture/culture/a63511308/lady-gaga-interview/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Elle的</em></a>新“问我任何东西”采访中，这位流行歌星被问及她即将发行的第八张专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lady-gaga-announces-new-album-mayhem-3832317">“ Mayhem”</a> ，并回答了有关她的个人和职业生活的问题。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/joker-folie-a-deux-review-lady-gaga-3790522"><b>“ Joker：FolieàDeux”评论：Lady Gaga在挑衅性的监狱音乐剧中闪耀</b></a></strong></li></ul><p>在聊天中的某一时刻，Gaga被问到：“您在音乐上承受的最大风险是什么？”</p><p>她回答说：“我认为做爵士乐是一个很大的风险。我认为人们以为我很疯狂。但我的意思是，您必须真正拥有一首很棒的歌，才能将其纳入《 American American Songbook》。</p><p> “所以我会说这是一个很大的风险，因为很多人不想让我这样做，但是我还是这样做了。”</p><p>在谈到她冒险进入新型和风格的愿望时，这位歌手继续说道：“我喜欢各种音乐，我觉得自己是音乐家的喜悦的一部分是您是学生。</p><p> “如果您不是学生，对我来说，那是一种无聊的探险。就像是探险家一样，但您真的不想找到任何东西。”您可以在这里观看完整的采访： </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Lady Gaga揭示了“ Mayhem”在声音上是艰苦而诗意的|问我什么|埃勒" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/o99ZykUPr2Y?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> Gaga与已故的爵士偶像<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tony-bennett">Tony Bennett</a> ：“ Cheek To Cheek”（2014年）和<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/tony-bennett-and-lady-gaga-love-for-sale-review-3058264">“ Love for Sales”</a> （2021）发行了两张<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/grammys">格莱美奖</a>的合作专辑。 2011年，贝内特（Bennett）录制了与加加（Gaga）的“二重奏II”系列的<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZPAmDULCVrU" target="_blank" rel="noopener">“女士是流浪汉”</a>的版本。</p><p>贝内特（Bennett）和加加（Gaga）于2021年在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tony-bennett-retires-from-performing-after-cancelling-remaining-tour-dates-3018434">前者宣布退休</a>后不久，在纽约市的无线电城音乐厅演出了两场特别节目。表演被捕获为一个名为<em>One上次的</em>电视节目，该电视节目<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/lady-gaga-tony-bennett-added-last-minute-emmy-nominees-for-concert-special-3282648">上次获得了杰出综艺特殊类别的艾美奖提名</a>。</p><p>此外， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tony-bennett-and-lady-gaga-to-share-mtv-unplugged-show-this-month-3106664">贝内特（Bennett）和加加（Gaga）为<em>MTV插头</em>提供了剥离的亲密现场套装</a>。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tony-bennett-dies-aged-96-3471623">贝内特（Bennett）于2023年去世</a>后，加加（Gaga） <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lady-gaga-shares-emotional-tribute-to-true-friend-tony-bennett-3475618">向音乐家和她的“真正朋友”分享了感人的致敬</a>。后来，她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lady-gaga-pays-tribute-to-tony-bennett-as-she-resumes-vegas-residency-3492594">在拉斯维加斯的一场居住表演中向他致敬</a>。</p><p>在另一篇文章中，这位明星写道：“每次我在舞台上演唱爵士音乐时，我都会庆祝你记住您为这个城市和整个世界所做的一切。” </p><figure id="attachment_3832329" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3832329" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3832329" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lady-Gaga-Mayhem-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="Lady Gaga&#39;Mayhem&#39;专辑艺术品。信用：出版" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lady-Gaga-Mayhem-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lady-Gaga-Mayhem-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lady-Gaga-Mayhem-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lady-Gaga-Mayhem-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lady-Gaga-Mayhem-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lady-Gaga-Mayhem-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lady-Gaga-Mayhem-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3832329" class="wp-caption-text"> Lady Gaga&#39;Mayhem&#39;专辑艺术品。信用：出版</figcaption></figure><p>Gaga的新专辑“ Mayhem”将于3月7日发行，此后从2020年代的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/lady-gaga-chromatica-album-review-2677590">“ Chromatoma”</a>和她的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lady-gaga-announces-joker-2-companion-album-harlequin-3796692">“ Harlequin”同伴唱片</a>（2024）发行。</p><p>她将于2月2日在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/grammys-nominations-2025-check-out-the-full-list-of-nominations-here-3811039">2025年格莱美颁奖典礼</a>上的商业休息期间，将在2月2日在2月2日首次亮相。这位歌手已经发行了单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-lady-gaga-dramatic-new-single-disease-3806194">“疾病”</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lady-gaga-reveals-die-with-a-smile-with-bruno-mars-huge-part-new-album-3824137">“带着微笑死亡”</a> 。</p><p>同时， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lady-gaga-describes-new-album-mayhem-as-utter-chaos-3832657">Gaga在最近的一次采访中将“混乱”描述为“混乱”</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/coachella-2025-lady-gaga-green-day-post-malone-travis-scott-lead-line-up-3814558">Gaga将于4月与Post Malone和Green Day一起在4月的Coachella 2025头条新闻</a>。她还将与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Billie-Eilish">Billie Ei</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Billie-Eilish">Lish</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Stevie-Nicks">Stevie Nicks</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Green-Day">Green Day</a>等人一起参加<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-lady-gaga-green-day-stevie-nicks-and-more-to-perform-at-la-wildfires-benefit-concert-3829759">LA Wildfires Benefit Concert的表演者之一</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lady-gaga-on-biggest-risk-shes-taken-in-music-people-